So then we got to fiat currency.

00:08:09.130 --> 00:08:11.460
And fiat currency,
as Jihee said,

00:08:11.460 --> 00:08:14.440
they were represented by
central bank notes, central bank

00:08:14.440 --> 00:08:16.285
reserves, and bank deposits.

00:08:16.285 --> 00:08:17.800
So there's three things.

00:08:17.800 --> 00:08:20.950
Does anybody want
to see if anybody

00:08:20.950 --> 00:08:22.480
listened in those classes?

00:08:22.480 --> 00:08:24.130
