central authority.

00:11:37.090 --> 00:11:38.620
So what if it gets copied?

00:11:38.620 --> 00:11:42.140
But the double spending
is the big issue.

00:11:42.140 --> 00:11:47.940
So how did he solve
it, or she solve it?

