00:41:52.900 --> 00:41:56.200
an incredible group of
Bitcoin Core developers,

00:41:56.200 --> 00:41:58.390
in part because
they just believe

00:41:58.390 --> 00:42:00.520
in it, in part that
some are funded

00:42:00.520 --> 00:42:04.530
by institutions like MIT.

00:42:04.530 --> 00:42:07.720
But it's still-- it's always
a challenge in a truly

00:42:07.720 --> 00:42:09.310
decentralized space.

00:42:09.310 --> 00:42:10.570
Who's going to fund--

00:42:10.570 --> 00:42:14.680
who's got the economic interest
to fund the continued updates

00:42:14.680 --> 00:42:15.850
