00:42:40.340 --> 00:42:41.510
money and risk.

00:42:41.510 --> 00:42:42.890
We talked about that.

00:42:42.890 --> 00:42:45.170
But it relies on a
system of ledgers,

00:42:45.170 --> 00:42:50.390
and it's always had a symbiotic
relationship with technology.

00:42:50.390 --> 00:42:53.450
The opportunities-- these
are the key opportunities,

00:42:53.450 --> 00:42:55.460
which I think any
thought fintech--

00:42:55.460 --> 00:42:59.060
