00:43:08.150 --> 00:43:10.750
The economic rents are high.

00:43:10.750 --> 00:43:13.730
There's 7 and 1/2 percent
of the economy is finance.

00:43:13.730 --> 00:43:16.340
Not all of the 7 and
1/2 percent is rents,

00:43:16.340 --> 00:43:19.470
