They might all use
Fidelity's product.

00:54:19.750 --> 00:54:24.780
Or they'll keep it
in-house or spin it off.

00:54:24.780 --> 00:54:27.790
I think they'll have to start
complying with any money

00:54:27.790 --> 00:54:28.290
laundering.

