Occasionally, you'll
see something--

00:55:04.860 --> 00:55:07.430
the Securities and Exchange
Commission or some other--

00:55:07.430 --> 00:55:09.240
maybe it will be in
Japan or elsewhere will

00:55:09.240 --> 00:55:11.310
be bringing more cases.

00:55:11.310 --> 00:55:14.670
And what will be interesting
in 2019 is to watch,

00:55:14.670 --> 00:55:17.580
does any of the
big ones go live?

00:55:17.580 --> 00:55:19.740
And I think this
will be a real test.

00:55:19.740 --> 00:55:21.990
Does Filecoin figure
out what to do?

